    "An Agentic AI system is an AI system that exhibits adaptability in achieving complex goals in complex environments with limited direct supervision [25].",
    "We particularly study the tradeoffs of supporting the Model Context Protocol (MCP) [8], an interoperability protocol for connecting AI applications to external systems."
  ]
